description: Returns a list of the available cache engines and their versions.

parameters.name: EngineVersion
parameters.description: The cache engine version to return. Example: 1.4.14

parameters.name: CacheParameterGroupFamily
parameters.description: The name of a specific cache parameter group family to return details for. Valid values are: memcached1.4 | memcached1.5 | memcached1.6 | redis2.6 | redis2.8 | redis3.2 | redis4.0 | redis5.0 | redis6.x | redis6.2 | redis7 | valkey7 Constraints: Must be 1 to 255 alphanumeric characters First character must be a letter Cannot end with a hyphen or contain two consecutive hyphens.

parameters.name: MaxRecords
parameters.description: The maximum number of records to include in the response. If more records exist than the specified MaxRecords value, a marker is included in the response so that the remaining results can be retrieved. Default: 100 Constraints: minimum 20; maximum 100.

nested_items.name: Marker
nested_items.description: Provides an identifier to allow retrieval of paginated results.

nested_items.name: CacheEngineVersions
nested_items.description: A list of cache engine version details. Each element in the list contains detailed information about one cache engine version.

nested_items.name: Engine
nested_items.description: The name of the cache engine.

nested_items.name: EngineVersion
nested_items.description: The version number of the cache engine.

nested_items.name: CacheParameterGroupFamily
nested_items.description: The name of the cache parameter group family associated with this cache engine.

nested_items.name: CacheEngineDescription
nested_items.description: The description of the cache engine.

nested_items.name: CacheEngineVersionDescription
nested_items.description: The description of the cache engine version.
